
Crossfire
---------

Crossfire is a fork of Openfire aimed at being secure, reliable, and easily configurable.

Release 0.6

- Continue to strip Openfire down to its minimum. Removed clustering, SSL, and S2S 
- Refactoring to minimize singletons, static classes, and inner classes (to all more easily unit test in future)

Release 0.5
- Rebranded as Crossfire
- Stripped out all plugins
